strings.Value: "Octavia, what are you doing? You should be ashamed of yourself!"
"Looks like Amiri is not in the mood for your jokes!"
"I don't infringe upon your freedom, but your behavior is terrible."
"Look what you've done! You upset Amiri for nothing!"
"Amiri, you are so strong! With you no monsters scare us! And this sword — ugh! It's probably heavier than I am! How do you lift it?"
{n}The barbarian smirks happily.{/n} "Yeah, not all can do it! You have to train! Hammer the enemy face to face... Or face to toothy snout... It's not like hurling spells from afar!"
"Your muscles are like stone! You could probably lift me with one hand! Do you think you could?" {n}Octavia moves closer to Amiri and runs her fingers along Amiri's shoulder.{/n}
"Listen, Octavia... Are you drunk or something? If I were a man, I'd think you are flirting with me!"
"Men, women, what's the difference? Don't you like me at all?"

{n}Amiri blushes a little.{/n} "Well... You are beautiful, of course... But I've never..." {n}Stopping short, the barbarian looks at you and Regongar.{/n} "Stop! You have {Name} and Regongar, go intertwine with them! And leave me out of your hanky-panky!"
{n}Regongar whispers to you softly,{/n} "Whoops, you shouldn't have said that... Here we go!"
{n}Octavia gives you a defiant stare.{/n} "'What am I doing?' Does that mean you don't like me flirting with somebody else? Well don't expect an apology. I'm not your slave!"
"Right, baby, don't embarrass our monster crusher! Look what you've done — she's blushing!"
"What?! Who, me? Nothing like that! Hell with this!" {n}Amiri turns away with indignation.{/n}
{n}Octavia shrugs, annoyed.{/n} "I'll do as I please! I'm a free person. No one tells me what to do!"
"And I think you've finally showed me your true face! Possessiveness and jealousy are written all over it!"
{n}The anger in Octavia's eyes gives way to embarrassment, and she looks away.{/n} "Me too... I don't know what got into me."
"I'll go get some air!" {n}The half-elf steps aside.{/n}

{n}Regongar shakes his head knowingly.{/n} "Don't worry, she can be like this. She doesn't mean it, just... She likes testing people's endurance. And the closer a person is to her, the harder she likes to push it. You just have to be patient."
"Teasing? What are you saying? Why would I tease you?"
{n}Octavia looks sheepishly at the barbarian.{/n} "I'm... sorry, Amiri, this was truly stupid."
"Oh dear... You shouldn't have said that. This is no joke for her — she'll shut you down after this. You know that freedom is everything for her."
{n}Regongar puts his arm around your shoulders.{/n} "But don't worry, I won't leave you!"
{n}Regongar puts his arm around your shoulders.{/n} "But don't worry, she'll come back around. Our girl needs some space, that's all."
"Easy, easy. It happens."
